\v 13 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômol n…ôhlan nian in t…ôm…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s kitat e n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha napin…ôp…ôn, m…®nol kitat k…®notuwa e n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha N…ôt…®n it…ôm in tolkeike p…®k.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Luk 22:53; Efes 2:2 \x*
