\v 26 n…ôghat…ôn …ôh in nalp…ôkau anion…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ômat…ôhluaig o net…ômim rafin aup…ôn ik…®n, m…ôto roiu …ôh Uhg…®n t…®nuhap…®k n…®p…ôt…®n k…ôm r…ôhan net…ômim.\x - \xo 1:26 \xt Rom 16:25-26; Efes 3:2-9 \x*
