\v 2 Iatol w…ôk n…ôhlan o n…®l…ôs-ip…ôr…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhat…ômat rafin, nian it…ômat nakot…®lp…®n w…®r n…®kit…ômat m…ôm…ô n…®kit…ômat otol kiti…ôh …ôm, k…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u in tatuwa nian nakoatolkeike it…ômat m…®n. K…ôn iatol w…ôk m…ôm…ô it…ômat rafin on…ôkotos n…®tun…ôn t…ôw…®r it…ôm otol n…®kit…ômat t…ôsan…ôn, k…ôn in otol m…®n m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…®tun w…®r n…ôghat…ôn pahrien r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm aup…ôn t…ômat…ôhluaig m…ôto roiu t…®net-ar…ôp. K…ôn nalp…ôkau…ôn anion …ôh, in Kristo,
