\p 
\v 2 It…ômat on…ôkot…ôk…ôike moat…ôghat-p…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n e n…ôfak…ôn e nian rafin. K…ôn nian onakoat…ôfak, r…ôhat…ômat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn ot…ôk…ôike m…ôtat…®g lan, k…ôn nian rafin ag…®n n…ôkot…ôk…ôike moat…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô n…®kit…ômat t…ôtagien o nat…®mnat it…ôm in t…ômol k…ôm it…ômat.\x - \xo 4:2 \xt Efes 6:18; Fil 4:6 \x*
\v 3 K…ôn io iakolkeike m…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike mot…ôfak m…®n ot…®mat m…®n, m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n oter…ôh e suat…®p m…ô ekot…ôn-iar…ôp nalp…ôkau anion…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n e Kristo. M…ôto-inu emat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn u inu k…ôn kahtos…®g-in-p…ôn io ron e kalapus.\x - \xo 4:3 \xt Rom 15:30; Efes 6:19 \x*
\v 4 Ot…ôfak m…ôm…ô iat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn …ôh t…ôtuat…®p k…ôn m…ôpi…ô w…®r tahmen …ôm m…ô ek…ôike mol mihin.
\p 
\v 5 It…ômat net…ôm noat…ôfak, p…ôs net…ôm k…ôsot…ôfak…ôn kotehm-p…ôn Iesu e nol…ôn m…®n r…ôhat…ômat, k…ôn e nian rafin on…ôkot…ôk…ôike moatehm w…®r m…ô nol…ôn, ne n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhat…ômat in otiuw Iaihlu…ô m…®n kotuwa o Iesu.\x - \xo 4:5 \xt Efes 5:15-16 \x*
\v 6 It…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike moat…ôghat w…®r k…ôm ilat e n…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôm u it…ôm t…ôw…®r k…ôn m…ôtehen, k…ôn p…ôs ilat okot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôh m…ô kot…ôw…®r. K…ôn it…ômat on…ôkot…ôk…ôike mot…®tun w…®r suat…®p m…®n o nuhalp…®n…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhalat it…ôm koat…ôtap…ôh o r…ôhat…ômat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn o Iesu.\x - \xo 4:6 \xt Efes 4:29; 1 Pita 3:15 \x*
\s1 Pol t…ômahl-ip…ôn t…ôs mil katian olat
\p 
\v 7-8 Etahl-ip…®n…ô pi…ôtat et…ôm t…ôw…®r, Tikikas, in tat…®mn…ô ot…ômat o nat k…ôiu …ôm m…ôm…ô in otamnus n…ôghat…ôn rafin r…ôhat…®mat k…ôm it…ômat, k…ôn in otol n…®kit…ômat t…ômeg…ôh. In pi…ôtat kit it…ôm io ekolkeike p…®k. Nian rafin in tat…ôtul mat…®p o nasitu…ôn lak e w…ôk r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.\x - \xo 4:7-8 \xt Efes 6:21-22 \x*
\v 9 In tat…®mn…ô ilau pi…ôtat Onesimas. Nian rafin in t…ôtahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Iesu, k…ôn it…®mat ekotolkeike p…®k in. In et…ômim kit r…ôhat…ômat. Ilau oku…ôn k…ôm it…ômat namnus…ôn r…ôha nat…®mnat rafin ik…®n-u.\x - \xo 4:9 \xt Flm 10-12 \x*
\s1 Namnun n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Pol t…ômuw…®n k…ôm ilat
\p 
\v 10 Aristakas in t…ôtat…®g e kalapus it…®mlau min. In t…ôtahl-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn w…®r k…ôm it…ômat. K…ôn Mak, in pia Panapas, in m…®n t…ôtahl-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn w…®r r…ôhan k…ôm it…ômat. It…ômat n…ônamotos r…ôk…®s r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn ron. Ok…ôm…ô in ot…®mn…ô r…ôhat…ômat ik…®n, k…ôn nakotit motuw…®n moatehm w…®r.\x - \xo 4:10 \xt W…ôk 12:12; 13:13; 15:37-39; 2 Tim 4:11 \x*
\v 11 K…ôn Josua Jastas, in m…®n t…ôtahl-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn w…®r r…ôhan k…ôm it…ômat. E noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel it…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô e Iesu, suah mil…ôhal …ôm …ôh, il…ôhal k…ôt…ôhalasitu lak o w…ôk r…ôha nego r…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn suah mil…ôhal …ôh, il…ôhal k…ôt…ôhalasitu p…®k lak e nian …ôskas…®k m…®n it…ôm tatuwa e r…ôhak n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.
\p 
\v 12 Epafras in r…ôhat…ômat kit et…ômim, in m…®n t…ôtahl-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn w…®r k…ôm it…ômat. In et…ômim kit nian rafin tatol w…ôk r…ôha Iesu Kristo, k…ôn e nian rafin in tat…ôfak …ôskas…®k ot…ômat. In tat…ôtap…ôh o Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô it…ômat onakoat…ôtul …ôskas…®k k…ôn mot…®m…ôt…ô mot…®tun w…®r nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike.
\v 13 Ek…®tun n…ôn…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô suah u in tatol w…ôk …ôskas…®k o nasitu…ôn et…ômat, ne net…ôm Laotisia, ne net…ôm Hierapolis.
\v 14 Tokita Luk et…ôm kitat kotolkeike p…®k, ne suah u Temas, ilau m…®n katuahl-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn w…®r k…ôm it…ômat.\x - \xo 4:14 \xt Kol 1:7; Flm 23-24 \x*
\p 
\v 15 Otahl-ip…ôn m…®n r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn w…®r k…ôm pi…ôtat ne w…®n…®tat m…®n …ôp…ôh Laotisia, ne p…ôtan …ôh Nimfa, ne net…ôm koat…ôfak e nian m…®n rafin …ôh r…ôhan ik…®n.
\v 16 M…ôto e nian on…ôkotafin r…ôk…®s r…ôhak naoa un, k…ôn mot…ôike motahl-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ôm Laotisia m…ô ilat okotafin m…®n k…ôm net…ômim r…ôha nim…ôfak …ôh-ik…®n. K…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh m…®n, it…ômat on…ôkot…ôk…ôike motafin m…®n naoa r…ôha net…ôm Laotisia.
\v 17 K…ôn it…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike mot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Akipas m…ôm…ô in ot…ôk…ôike mol rafin w…ôk it…ôm I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat in t…ômos-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô otol.\x - \xo 4:17 \xt Flm 2 \x*
\p 
\v 18 Io Pol, iatos pen mat…ôte …ôm e nelm…ôk n…ôghat…ôn u r…ôha n…ôn…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat. Sotaluin…ôn sen it…ôm k…ôm…ôlis io lan e kalapus. P…ôs Uhg…®n otasitu et…ômat k…ôn mawte-in r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn t…ôtat…®g ot…ômat.\x - \xo 4:18 \xt 1 Kor 16:21 \x* 
